# Summarizing Data

## `tbl_summary()` : table summary (1/2)

-   What if I want one of those fancy summary tables that are at the top of most research articles? (lovingly called "Table 1")

::: columns
::: {.column width="50%"}


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(gtsummary)
tbl_summary(dds.discr2)
```
:::


:::

::: {.column width="50%"}


::: {.cell}
